%*! intToFloatOperator(Operator)

Operators that take an integer and return a float.

Args:
    - Operator: An operator that takes an integer and returns a float.
*%

%*! floatUnOperator(Operator)

Unary operators that take a float and return a float.

Args:
    - Operator: A unary operator that takes a float and returns a float.
*%

%*! floatFloatFloatOperator(Operator)

Binary operators that take two floats and return a float.

Args:
    - Operator: A binary operator that takes two floats and returns a float.
*%

%*! floatBinOperator(Operator)

Binary operators that take at least one float and return a float.

Args:
    - Operator: A binary operator that takes at least one float and returns a float.
*%
